                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philada.</placeName>\n                                        <date>June 19<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1849</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Sir<add>?</add></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">It is with extreme regret that I<lb/> am\n                                        constrained by circumstances to request you to\n                                        discontinue<lb/> my subscription to the Occident for the\n                                        present. Justice<lb/> to my known opinions as to the\n                                        necessity of sustaining it<lb/> demands a remark. My <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">Responsibilities\n                                        increase</hi><lb/> with no corresponding improvement in\n                                        income. The<lb/> same “row fortune” that prescribes such\n                                        narrow limits<lb/> to the sphere of usefulness of many\n                                        warmly desirous of<lb/> serving their God &amp; their fellow\n                                        man, has ever <del>but</del> restrained<lb/> me with\n                                        stringent bonds. Altho' knowing<lb/> it is unusual to\n                                        withdraw a subscription until arrears<lb/> are paid, yet I\n                                        also feel myself unwarranted in increas=<lb/>ing an\n                                        indebtedness from which there is no immediate prospect<lb/>\n                                        of release. When I say I regret this necessity,<lb/> it has\n                                        no idle meaning, &amp; is enhanced by the fact<lb/> of\n                                        having been one of your subscribers since the issue<lb/> of\n                                        the first number. Most cheerfully<lb/> will I renew the\n                                        Occident at the earliest moment practi=<lb/>=cable, and it\n                                        will ever continue to have my warmest<lb/> wishes for\n                                        success.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Your friend &amp; well wisher</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(7)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Alfred F. Jones</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3np1x16p/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
